description:
Powerslide is a driving game like no other, with screaming fast graphics, drive anywhere 3D modeled environments, and gameplay that will keep you glued to your screen for an unhealthy length of time. It looks wicked, and the physics are awesome ? it feels totally real to drive.

This is one of my favourite racing games ever, it's fun but it gets pretty hard.
I've incuded Xpadder with a profile for the Xbox360 controller.

I highly recommend using a gamepad, but each to their own.

No major rig required to play this game as it came out in 1998, but has very nice graphics if you keep it the way I have set it up.

OS: Windows XP / Vista / 7 

Note:

I have included my own music to bump up the atmosphere of the game, but I've included the original soundtracks as well.

